@node __dpmi_get_selector_increment_value, dpmi
@subheading Syntax

@example
#include <dpmi.h>

int __dpmi_get_selector_increment_value(void);
@end example

@subheading Description

Please refer to @ref{DPMI Specification} for details on DPMI
function call operation.  Also see @ref{DPMI Overview} for general
information.

DPMI function AX = 0x0003

@subheading Return Value

The value to return to each selector allocated by
__dpmi_allocate_ldt_descriptors to get the next one.
